Package recursionLimit

Class TestRecursionLimit

  • java.lang.Object
    • recursionLimit.TestRecursionLimit

  • public class TestRecursionLimit
extends java.lang.Object
    Tests the effect of recursion limit by testing arrays with sizes ranging from 20,000 to 10,000,000. Uses recursion limits ranging from 2-300 with increment 2, resulting in about 3000 entries For each recursion limit / array size combination, uses 3 int arrays with randomly filled with numbers ranging from 0-100, sorts each array individually, then takes the average of the sorting time
